            <title>[FLUME-2568] Additional fix for TestReliableSpoolingFileEventReader</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FLUME-2568</link>
                <project id="12311321" key="FLUME">Flume</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;TestReliableSpoolingFileEventReader needs some more modification in addition to the fix provided in &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FLUME-2505&quot; title=&quot;Test added in FLUME-2502 is flaky&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;FLUME-2505&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;FLUME-2505&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
1) Needed to add semaphore2 to ensure that new file gets created before the second listing, without this readEventsForFilesInDir() can complete before the new file gets created&lt;br/&gt;
2) had to remove renameTo and instead create the newfile, for the directory listing to pick the new file &lt;/p&gt;</description>
